name: victorian banner
description:
••••••••••   15 feet of charm   •••••••••••

the victorian banner is made with:
• vintage hankies 
• recycled canvas
• vintage lace 
• vintage napkins
• muslin
• cotton twill
• linen
• white cotton twine

the victorian banner always has:
• white
• cream
• off-white
• small amounts of soft color
• embroidery

the victorian banner is perfect for:
• room decor
• party decor
• weddings
• photo shoots
• baby nursery

always one-of-a-kind. the banner you receive will not be the one pictured, but one that is made in the same style with many of the same fabrics. 

this banner cannot be washed, as it's too delicate.

name: bright patchwork banner
description:
the patchwork banner is the most popular style; it's colorful, light, fun, and brings sunshine to a room. 
great for parties too, indoors or outside.

15 feet long, each one is unique. fabric is sewn to cotton twine with whatever thread color is available; it's a grab-bag on a string.

we don't recommend washing because these are delicate.

*we mean it when we say we don't throw anything away. if we hadn't kept to our word, this fabulous banner would never have been created.
